WEBVTT

00:04:26.667 --> 00:04:30.309
and to get clean clothing, food,

00:04:30.333 --> 00:04:32.476
hygiene items.

00:04:32.500 --> 00:04:37.518
Just love and compassion
was seen everywhere.

00:04:37.542 --> 00:04:41.726
So I turned back and I responded
to him and I said,

00:04:41.750 --> 00:04:44.393
"Restoring human dignity.

00:04:44.417 --> 00:04:46.351
That's what we're doing."

00:04:46.375 --> 00:04:48.809
I don't think he expected
that answer from me,

00:04:48.833 --> 00:04:50.226
because he took a step back

00:04:50.250 --> 00:04:53.226
and then approached me again and said,

00:04:53.250 --> 00:04:57.601
"Sister, if I had a magic wand,

00:04:57.625 --> 00:04:59.833
what would that magic wand do for you?"